Maven project

2 folders under src:
main- is use to write the main code for application
test- is used to write the code for testing the application

inside test folder:
java- our java code which we write to test our applicatin
resources- we keep properties, test data, etc
config- we store configuration file
utils- we keep utilities classes we need in the project

Framework- it allow  you write, reuse and mantain your code with minimal efforts.

Maven- it is a build tool

pom.xml

POM- page object model

